  <Identity>
    <Name>StingProductCodes</Name>
    <Definition>Product codes for the seventh segment (PROD) of the STING 8-segment tag. The PROD code names the *kind* of element — AHU, FCU, distribution board, basin, sprinkler, etc. The set is corporate-locked to give STING its proprietary tag grammar; projects extend by adding new codes only through schema-release governance, never inline. Project-specific equipment catalogues (manufacturer / model) are kept out of this enum and ride Pset_ManufacturerTypeInformation natively.</Definition>
    <IfdGuid>uuid:a1d15c11-0001-4001-9000-000000000004</IfdGuid>
    
  </Identity>

  <Governance>
    <Scope>corporate</Scope>
    <Origin>baseline</Origin>
    <SinceVersion>5.0.0</SinceVersion>
    <Maintainer>STING Tools (Planscape)</Maintainer>
    <StandardsBasis>STING tag config v5.0 (Data/STING_TAG_CONFIG_v5_0_*.csv); CIBSE Guide A/B/C product taxonomies; Uniclass 2015 Pr-table cross-reference</StandardsBasis>
  </Governance>

